text:
Great pisang! Crunchy batter, soft and sweet middle. Many other deep fried items available. Heard mini donuts are good too.
Located in Bedok Corner Food Center.

Favourite stall to get goreng Pisang. Jemput Pisang is also my favourite. Fried green bean and various kueh kueh.

Mostly 3 various pieces for $2.50. Some would cost $2.70 like Pisang tanduk.

Affordable snack to be eaten anytime of the day. Best is they are open very early in the morning.
Above average Goreng Pisang along with a fun variety of choices! You will easily be able to buy $2 for 3 pieces of your choice. An experience to behold üëçüèª
Very nice variety of bananas to be amde into goreng pisang. So diverse! Nice n delicious. Old makcik very friendly and nice, super lovely! Also have many other kueh and nasi lemak and epok epok
